title: In Tech: NFL on TuneIn, home jukebox and Uber deliveries
text: In Tech: NFL on TuneIn, home jukebox and Uber deliveries By Associated Press | October 14, 2015 @ 10:41 am \n FILE - In this Sept. 27, 2015 file photo, St. Louis Rams tight end Jared Cook, left, can\'t catch the ball in the end zone as Pittsburgh Steelers cornerback Ross Cockrell defends during the fourth quarter of an NFL football game, in St. Louis. Internet radio service TuneIn is adding live play-by-play audio coverage of all NFL games to its $8 a month premium subscription. (AP Photo/Billy Hurst, File)\n
